{{#> base}}
    <h2>Your One-Time Password (OTP)</h2>
    <p>Hello {{username}},</p>
    <p>Your one-time password (OTP) is:</p>
    
    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <div style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 5px; color: #007bff;">
            {{otp}}
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <p>This OTP will expire in {{expiration}}.</p>
    
    <p>If you did not request this OTP, please ignore this email or contact support if you have concerns.</p>
    
    <p>Best regards,<br>The {{companyName}} Team</p>
{{/base}} 